<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Tangram Technology Limited</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #10B981;
            --primary-dark: #059669;
            --primary-light: #34D399;
            --secondary: #3B82F6;
            --accent: #60A5FA;
            --dark: #2c3e50;
            --light: #ecf0f1;
            --gradient-green: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981 0%, #34D399 100%);
            --gradient-blue: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6 0%, #60A5FA 100%);
            --gradient-tech: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981 0%, #059669 100%);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* About Us Section - Modern Design */
        .about-section {
            position: relative;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #e8f5f1 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Animated Background Elements */
        .about-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: -200px;
            right: -200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 20s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        .about-section::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            bottom: -150px;
            left: -150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 15s infinite ease-in-out reverse;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg);
            }
            33% {
                transform: translate(30px, -30px) rotate(120deg);
            }
            66% {
                transform: translate(-20px, 20px) rotate(240deg);
            }
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 1600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .about-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* Left Side - Title Section */
        .about-title-section {
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-label {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--gradient-tech);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 24px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
            animation: slideInLeft 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .about-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            animation: slideInLeft 0.8s ease-out 0.2s backwards;
        }

        .about-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -15px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100px;
            height: 6px;
            background: var(--gradient-green);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        /* Decorative Elements */
        .title-decoration {
            position: absolute;
            top: -30px;
            left: -40px;
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1), rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.05));
            border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 30% 30% 70% 70%;
            z-index: -1;
            animation: morphing 8s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes morphing {
            0%, 100% {
                border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 30% 30% 70% 70%;
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }
            50% {
                border-radius: 70% 30% 30% 70% / 70% 70% 30% 30%;
                transform: rotate(180deg);
            }
        }

        /* Right Side - Content Section */
        .about-text-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px 35px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) inset;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out 0.4s backwards;
        }

        .about-text-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--gradient-tech);
        }

        .company-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .about-description {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
            text-align: justify;
            position: relative;
        }

        .about-description::first-letter {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            float: left;
            line-height: 0.8;
            margin: 10px 10px 0 0;
            background: var(--gradient-tech);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        /* Stats Section */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 18px 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .stat-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: var(--gradient-tech);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        }

        .stat-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.05;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: var(--gradient-tech);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Highlights Section */
        .highlights {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .highlight-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .highlight-item:hover {
            background: #e9f7f3;
            transform: translateX(5px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
        }

        .highlight-icon {
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            background: var(--gradient-tech);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .highlight-text {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInRight {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 968px) {
            .about-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
            }

            .about-title {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }

            .about-text-section {
                padding: 35px;
            }

            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }

            .highlights {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .about-section {
                padding: 60px 15px;
            }

            .about-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .about-text-section {
                padding: 25px;
            }

            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .title-decoration {
                display: none;
            }
        }

        /* Loading Animation */
        .about-section > * {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out backwards;
        }

        .stat-card {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out backwards;
        }

        .stat-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .stat-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
        .stat-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

        .highlight-item {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out backwards;
        }

        .highlight-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.9s; }
        .highlight-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1.0s; }
        .highlight-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.1s; }
        .highlight-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-content">
            
            <!-- Left Side - Title -->
            <div class="about-title-section">
                <div class="title-decoration"></div>
                <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
                <h1 class="about-title">ABOUT US</h1>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Side - Content -->
            <div class="about-text-section">
                <p class="about-description">
                    <span class="company-name">Tangram Technology Limited</span> is a leading provider of comprehensive solutions across various industries, including electronics, mold manufacturing, plastic injection, metal punching, air compressors, and other specialized machinery. With a state-of-the-art R&D center in Shenzhen, China, and manufacturing facilities in Zhongshan, China, and Dhaka, Bangladesh, Tangram is committed to delivering high-quality, reliable, and innovative products.
                </p>

                <!-- Stats -->
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">3</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Global Facilities</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">17+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Quality Assured</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Highlights -->
                <div class="highlights">
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <div class="highlight-icon">🔬</div>
                        <span class="highlight-text">State-of-the-art R&D Center</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <div class="highlight-icon">🏭</div>
                        <span class="highlight-text">Advanced Manufacturing</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <div class="highlight-icon">🌏</div>
                        <span class="highlight-text">Global Operations</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <div class="highlight-icon">✨</div>
                        <span class="highlight-text">Innovation Focused</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
